      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver that's ready to work for you? This vehicle is in honest, fair condition and has plenty of life left in it! It shows some character from its time on the road, but it starts right up and handles smoothly. It\u2019s a great opportunity to own a dependable car at a fantastic price\u2014perfect for someone who values functionality and value!",
